I Used Topices and Technologies 
-> Mediator and CQRS  Design Pattern 
-> Fluent Validation 
-> Localization
-> Logging with Serilog 
-> JWT Token & Refresh Token to Activate Expired Access Token 
-> Dealing With DB Components like StoredProcedure , Function and Views 
-> Exception Middleware 
-> ActionFilters 
-> Generic Repository 
-> UnitOfWork 
-> Confirming&Sending Mails 
-> Reset Password with Sending Code to Email 
-> Specification Design Pattern 
-> Uploading Files 
-> Authentication & Authorization Using (Roles & Policies)
-> Unified Response For All End Points 
